<li>Alphabetical Listing of Law Firms
<li>United States Government Servers<br>
	<cite>Most U.S. Government sites can be reached through this link. Recent
	Supreme Court decisions are available; at the time of writing, 	there was less than 		a three day wait between the time a decision was handed down and the time it 		appeared on the net.</cite>
<li>State Government Servers
<li>Law Journals on the WWW
<li>Non-U.S. Law Sites<br>
	<cite>This entry includes links to sites relating to countries such  as Australia, Canada, 		The Czech Republic (including daily news), 	Germany, Israel, Ireland and many 			more.</cite>
<li>International & Environmental Law
</ul><br>
