<h2><a name = "QL"> QuickLaw (QL) Passwords for Law Students </a></h2></center>
<p>
QuickLaw has re-activated all educational passwords for 1995-96. All upper year and graduate students who already have a QL password should have  access to QL as of September 1995. If you experience any problems with your password, please call QL at (416) 862-7656.
<p>	
QL's computer-based sign-up program is available for all first year and new  students. First year students will receive their passwords during their QL training sessions prior to library assignment  #3. The dates and times of these sessions will be posted in the Library shortly. 
 <p>
Graduate and new  students can sign on to QL in the computer lab. You will receive your password when you sign on for the first time.  Come to the circulation desk for the sign-on instructions. QL training for new and graduate students will be available shortly.  Look for notices in Headnotes and LawLink . 
