</ul>
Move the cursor to any one of the items on the list and click the mouse button, you will then be taken directly to that particular site
<p>
Students are urged to access these sites via Netscape and explore all that is available. Surfing  the NET is one way of discovering what is out there. The Internet is changing daily and one of the best way to keep up with the changes is to go surfing often.
<p>
<b>NCSA Telnet</b> is another software package that allows you to connect to various sites on the Internet and retrieve files. (Next month's issue of Lawlink will include a list of resources accessable through NCSA Telnet)
