<h3>September 1994, Volume 1 Number 2</h3>
<h2>Contents</h2>
<dl>
<dd><a href = "v1n2.htm #discussion">Discussion Lists on the Internet</a>
<dd><a href = "v1n2.htm #library">Library Announcements</a>
<dd><a href = "v1n2.htm #mail">Institutional Electronic Mail</a>
