<H2><A NAME="b"></A>B</H2>

<DT><B>Banking Law Journal</B> </DT>

<DD>Westlaw WGL-BLJ from v.104, 1987 </DD>

<DT><B>Banking Policy Report</B> </DT>

<DD>Westlaw BNKPR from v.11 no.5, 1992 </DD>

