<DD>BNKDEV (not in ALLREV group file) from 1984 </DD>

<DD>Westlaw BKRDEVJ from v.1, 1984 </DD>

<DT><B>Baylor Law Review</B> </DT>

<DD>Lexis BAYLOR from 1993 </DD>

<DD>Westlaw BLRLR from v.33, 1981 </DD>

