<head>
<title>University of Toronto Faculty of Law Review: Call for submissions</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#ffffff" link="#0000ff" vlink="#4040ad">
<center>
<table cellpadding=15>
<tr>
<td><h1>University<br>of Toronto<br>Faculty of<br>Law Review</h1></td>
<td><img align=center src="../icons/utcrest.gif" alt="U of T Crest"></td>
<td><h1>Revue de<br>droit de<br>l'Universit&eacute;<br>de Toronto</h1></td></tr></table><p>
[<a href="http://www.utoronto.ca/">University of Toronto</a>] [<a href="http://www.law.utoronto.ca/">Faculty of Law</a>] [<a href="http://www.law-lib.utoronto.ca/law-review/">Law Review</a>]
<hr width=80% noshade>
<h2>Call for submissions</h2></center>

The University of Toronto Faculty of Law Review is now accepting submissions of articles, book reviews, notes and comments from law students (including articling students) across the country.
<p>
Send articles, book reviews, notes and comments to:
<p>
<b>The Editors<br>
University of Toronto Faculty of Law Review<br>
78 Queen's Park<br>
Toronto, Ontario<br>
M5S 2C5<br>
(416) 978-1075</b>
<p>
The deadline for articles to be published in volume 55(2) and 55(3), is <b>January 20th, 1997.</b> Volume 55(3) is the Special Symposium Issue <cite>The Fifteenth Anniversary of The Charter</cite>.  Any questions or comments can be addressed to David Crerar or Melanie Shishler, editors-in-chief of the University of Toronto Faculty of Law Review.
<p><br><hr width=50% noshade><p><br>
<center><h2>Ecrivez-nous!</h2></center>

La Revue de la facult&eacute; de droit de l'universit&eacute; de Toronto recherche prsentement des articles, des critiques litt&eacute;raires, des notes et des commentaires provenant des &eacute;tudiants et &eacute;tudiantes en droit a travers le Canada.
<p>
Envoyer vos articles, critiques litt&eacute;raires, notes et commentaires aux:
<p>
R&eacute;dacteurs<br>
Revue de la facult&eacute; de droit de l'universit&eacute; de Toronto<br>
78 Queen's Park<br>
Toronto, Ontario<br>
M5S 2C5<br>
(416) 978-1075<br>
<p>
<b>Date-Limite:  le 20 septembre, 1996.</b>
<p>
<hr width=80% noshade>
