<li><a name="fifty">L. Sarna,</a> <i>supra</i>, note 16, &agrave; la p. 5--22; <cite>Landmark Leaseholds Ltd. v. Royal Bank of Canada</cite> (1989), 79 Sask. R. 38, aux pp. 41 et 42 (Q.B.).



