<li><a name="fifty"><cite>Sylvie Grondin v. Caf&eacute;t&eacute;ria I.C.S. et C.S.S.T. Richelieu Salaberry</cite></a>, [1991] C.A.L.P. 854 at 859; see also <cite>Plante v. Entreprises Jacques Marquis</cite>, [1991] (10) C.A.L.P. 11810--08--8905.
<p>
