<p>
<li><a name="seventy4"><i>Ibid.</i> ss. 43(4), (6), (7), (8) and (9).</a>
<p>
<li><a name="seventy5"><i>Ibid.</i></a> Section 20 provides for the appointment of a health and safety
adjudicator by Order-in-Council to adjudicate issues arising out of the <cite>Act</cite>.
<p>
<li><a name="seventy6">Telephone Interview with V. Stelmaszynski</a> (23 August 1994) Toronto. He is Legal Counsel, Office of Adjudication, Ontario Ministry of Labour.
<p>
