people and not all Jewish people was still discrimination based upon creed.
<p>
<li><a name="one08">(1989), 59 D.L.R. (4th) 321</a> at pages 337--39. This decision has now been followed in cases such as <cite>Re B.C. Telephone Co. and Telecommunications Workers Union</cite> (1990), 15 L.A.C. (4th) 146.
