<DOCHDR>
http://www.law-lib.utoronto.ca:80/law-review/utlr53-1/bowker.htm 128.100.167.100 19970109122238 text/html 179372
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 12:22:17 GMT
