<p>
<li><a name="one77">(1991), 62 C.C.C. (3d) 481 (Alta. C.A.)</a> one judge dissenting in the result.
<p>
<li><a name="one78"><i>Ibid</i>.</a> at 504--507. The Court took a broad purposive approach to the <cite>Charter</cite> rights rather than a narrow technical one.
<p>
<li><a name="one79">(1990), 55 C.C.C. (3d) 551 (B.C.C.A.).</a>
