<li><a name="sixty9">To illustrate,</a> the fee structures in Canadian REITs (percentage amount may differ), Counsel Management Services Inc., the manager of Counsel REIT, is entitled to the following fees:
<blockquote>
(a)   Annual management fee based on adjusted unit holders' equity:<br>
Up to $75 million 1.75%<br>
Between $75 and $125 million 1.50%<br>
Between $125 and $250 million 1.25%<br>
In excess of  $250 million 1.00%<br>
(b)   Fee of 1.75\% of the total acquisition price of any purchase of  real property\newline<br>
(c)   Fee of 0.25\% of the total disposition price of any sale of real property</blockquote>
