<p>
<li><a name="ninety9"><i>Supra</i></a> note 41 at 7.
<p>
<li><a name="onehundred">The pre-tax equivalent</a> yield is not static. The pre-tax equivalent yield will change over time as the tax shelter benefits (i.e. CCA and interest deductions) decrease.
<p>
<li><a name="one01">Ward,</a> <i>supra</i> note 33 at 8.
<p>
<li><a name="one02">Young,</a> <i>supra</i> note 4 at 1.
<p>
<li><a name="one03"><i>Supra</i></a> note 41 at 9.
<p>
