<li><a name="one98">As a result</a> of the increased institutional control of the Canadian real estate market relative to the U.S. marketplace, it is anticipated that demand for the REIT vehicle will be greater in Canada in the short term as this vehicle represents a mechanism to allow these institutions to liquidate their distressed real estate
portfolios.
