<li><a name="one01"><cite>Sobeys Inc.</cite></a> v. <cite>Nova Scotia (Attorney General)</cite> (1992), 112 N.S.R. (2d) 205 (T.D.), rev'd (1993), 120 N.S.R. (2d) 392 (C.A.) [hereinafter <cite>Sobeys</cite>].
