<p>
<li><a name="one64">(<i>sub nom.</i></a> <cite>Indian Refining Co. v. Bollinger</cite>) 168 N.E. 886 (S.C. Ill. 1929).
<p>
<li><a name="one65"><cite>Standard Oil Co</cite>.</a> v. <cite>Bollinger</cite>, 169 N.E. 236 (S.C. Ill. 1929). See also <cite>Agni Motor Fuel Co</cite>. v. <cite>Kinney</cite>, 172 N.E. 39 (S.C. Ill. 1930).
<p>
<li><a name="one66"><i>Ibid</i>. at 237.</a>
<p>
<li><a name="one67">180 N.E. 396</a> (S.C. Ill. 1932) [hereinafter <cite>Standard Oil</cite>].
<p>
<li><a name="one68">187 N.E. 657 (S.C. Ill. 1933).</a>
<p>
<li><a name="one69"><i>Ibid</i>. at 659.</a>
