<li><a name="thirty7">See P. Jull,</a> &quot;Greenland: Lessons of Self-Government and Development&quot; (1979) 7:8 Northern Perspectives 4; H.C. Gullov, &quot;Home Rule in Greenland&quot; (1981) 3 Inuit Studies 131.
