<li><a name="ninety1">This is</a> the acronym for the Designated Inuit Organization, which is either the Tungavik Federation, the central agency in charge of implementing and monitoring the <cite>Agreement</cite>, or organizations designated by the Tungavik. See <cite>Agreement</cite>, <i>supra</i> note 2 at Art. 1.
