<li><a name="one27">Ontario, Royal Commission on Violence in the Communications Industry,</a> <cite>Report: Approaches, Conclusions and Recommendations</cite>, vol. 1 (Toronto: Queen's Printer 1977) at 53.
<p>
<li><a name="one28">T.H.A. van der Voort,</a> <cite>Television Violence: A Child's-Eye View</cite> (Amsterdam: North-Holland Publishing, 1986) at 101.
<p>
<li><a name="one29"><cite>Oakes</cite></a>, <i>supra</i> note 100 at 139, citing <cite>Big M</cite>, <i>supra</i> note 78 at 352.
